{"tid":1361362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小心ZG頭救護車","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:13:28.000Z","uid":79249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a91ae2733204d9ec9f6e724f0659c5e32fae710a","tid":1361362,"uid":79249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">駐港部隊確認：網傳ZG救護車隸屬解放軍　有關救護車的5件事</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/33263/%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3zg%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%B8%E5%B1%AC%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E7%9A%845%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F33263%2F%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3zg%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259A%25B8%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D-%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%259A%25845%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0PrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b69ff6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/33263/%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3zg%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%B8%E5%B1%AC%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E7%9A%845%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚我老豆冇喇喇叫我唔好再去遊行，<br />\n<br />\n因為佢有個朋友個朋友係黑警，<br />\n<br />\n叫身邊人唔好去遊行，<br />\n<br />\n話會有解放軍落嚟捉示威者上大陸。<br />\n<br />\n信不信由你，我自己唔太信會有呢啲事發生。<br />\n<br />\n只係突然間記得<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍ZG字頭白車</span></span></strong>單新聞，<br />\n<br />\n想提一提大家。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">自行判斷係唔係真</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無論點都好，出到去行要記得：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要走一齊走，要留一齊留</span></span><br />\n<br />\n_________________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">除港奸傀儡 肅魔鬼警隊</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件\n\n5大訴求：\n1. 立即撤回送中條例\n2. 除消暴動定義\n3. 不再追究義士\n4. 成立獨立調查\n5. 真雙普選\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"825877435bdc157f74ba7a6a109944625bd56624","tid":1361362,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2758052519646851e10164b6339061a1ac8dc619","tid":1361362,"uid":79249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">除港奸傀儡 肅魔鬼警隊</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件\n\n5大訴求：\n1. 立即撤回送中條例\n2. 除消暴動定義\n3. 不再追究義士\n4. 成立獨立調查\n5. 真雙普選\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"738b600b27154540f700c67e8deed32b226cb13b","tid":1361362,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+